Third submission! Between work and picking up rhythm games while still trying for runs, I busted my wrist and fingers up. Oops. Took two weeks off doing any runs, but I'm glad to be back to climbing my way closer to my next goal: a sub 40 time! My time away from the game definitely rusted up some of my fundamentals that got me killed more than I liked, but I'm feeling overall more consistent. Here's to dying less and breaking into the 30s!
